Component Page

Package name:
fastn-community.github.io/site-doc
To use ke-value component on your web package, add below into FASTN.ftd file:
null
-- fastn.dependency: fastn-community.github.io/site-doc

-- fastn.dependency: fastn-community.github.io/site-doc
Once above dependency is added, then import it inside your .ftd files.
null
-- import: fastn-community.github.io/site-doc

-- import: fastn-community.github.io/site-doc
Example 1: Basic usage
Input
null
-- site-doc.key-value:
key: -- import:
value: fastn-community.github.io/site-doc

-- site-doc.key-value:
key: -- import:
value: fastn-community.github.io/site-doc
Output
null
-- import: fastn-community.github.io/site-doc

-- import: fastn-community.github.io/site-doc

Fields / attributes

Below are details of all fields / attributes of this component.
key
This is a default attribute of the key-value component, used to add a key to it.
Attribute name
Type
Default / Optional
key
String
Default
value
This is a default attribute of the key-value component, used to add a value to the key and appears in a row to key.
Attribute name
Type
Default / Optional
value
String
Default
